replies.body:
Her lore surely will. Looking at this text, pretty sure Ahri is vastayan and it seems that there are 3 grades. 

Grade 1: very strong animalistic features.
Example: {{champion:107}} 
Maybe even Rammus is one, it gets mentioned that there are short limbed ones in shurima. And we still don't know what he is exactly, even after the shurima update. And Urf seems to be one too.

Grade 2: human looking with some animal characteristics
Example: {{champion:103}} 

Grade 3: shape shifter
Example: {{champion:76}} 

I think that was a pretty elegant solution to explain these champions.
